{"tid":1631393,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再次證明水能救港","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:02.000Z","uid":41584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfb856b7b960382325e3aaa173b09b4e99749204","tid":1631393,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"上次講完我地水系既消防同海關會係救港既紀律部隊，今日我地偉大既消防就再加一分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/376552872550155/posts/1134133246792110?sfns=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F376552872550155%2Fposts%2F1134133246792110%3Fsfns%3D1&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL7ktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=4a28b2f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/376552872550155/posts/1134133246792110?sfns=1</a><br />\n快啲發揚水系魔法，還我真<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>漁港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c308699094616f19f15fa8bafa1514922e52836d","tid":1631393,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"大雨到仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce58755e56dea325e3ad0fd1b26c1812a484718e","tid":1631393,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:27:37.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d168cb01d0015cb6729bd427d12986419d2cd22e","tid":1631393,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:31:38.000Z","msg":"解決裝修分歧及文宣方法：十八區爆買日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631347\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631347</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a45bb6c78eb1dac2a487985a6755b03fe18a6a8","tid":1631393,"uid":41584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:02.000Z","msg":"落雨啦！香港有救啦！"}]}